---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Paid Consultation | Kinga Dow - Expert Retention Marketing Strategy"
  description="Book a 1-on-1 paid consultation with Kinga Dow. Get personalized retention marketing strategy, Klaviyo audit, and actionable recommendations for your e-commerce brand."
>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="hero-gradient relative overflow-hidden">
    <!-- Decorative circle pattern - left side -->
    <div class="absolute -left-20 top-16 w-[380px] h-[380px] opacity-30 pointer-events-none">
      <img src="/images/home/decorative/bg-circle-left.png" alt="" class="w-full h-full object-contain" aria-hidden="true" />
    </div>

    <!-- Decorative circle pattern - bottom right -->
    <div class="absolute -right-16 -bottom-16 w-[300px] h-[300px] opacity-20 pointer-events-none">
      <img src="/images/home/decorative/bg-circle.png" alt="" class="w-full h-full object-contain" aria-hidden="true" />
    </div>

    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-12 md:py-20 relative z-10">
      <div class="text-center max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <!-- Label: Gold uppercase -->
        <span class="animate-on-scroll fade-in-up font-aktiv text-kd-gold font-medium text-[14px] leading-[17px] tracking-[1.4px] mb-4 block uppercase">
          Paid Consultation
        </span>

        <!-- H1 - Hero -->
        <h1 class="animate-on-scroll fade-in-up delay-100 font-aktiv text-kd-navy text-[28px] md:text-[48px] font-bold leading-[36px] md:leading-[60px] tracking-[1.4px] md:tracking-[2.4px] mb-6">
          Get Expert AI Strategy<br />For Your E-Commerce Brand
        </h1>

        <!-- Subtitle: Script font -->
        <p class="animate-on-scroll fade-in-up delay-200 font-script text-kd-gold text-[24px] md:text-[36px] leading-[30px] md:leading-[44px] tracking-[1.2px] md:tracking-[1.8px] mb-6">
          1 on 1 with Kinga
        </p>

        <!-- Body text -->
        <p class="animate-on-scroll fade-in-up delay-300 font-montserrat font-light text-black text-[16px] md:text-[18px] mb-8 max-w-[800px] mx-auto leading-[26px] md:leading-[30px] tracking-[1.6px] md:tracking-[1.8px]">
          Learn how to implement AI into your marketing strategy from an expert who pioneered the first AI-native retention marketing agency. Walk away with actionable AI workflows tailored to your business.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Package Details Section -->
  <section class="py-12 md:py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-10 md:gap-16 items-center">

        <!-- Left: Package Card -->
        <div class="animate-on-scroll fade-in-up">
          <div class="bg-kd-cream rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-10 relative overflow-hidden">
            <!-- Decorative gold accent -->
            <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-1 bg-kd-gold"></div>

            <!-- Package name -->
            <h2 class="font-aktiv text-kd-navy text-[22px] md:text-[26px] font-semibold tracking-[1.1px] mb-2">
              AI Strategy Session
            </h2>

            <!-- Duration -->
            <p class="font-montserrat text-kd-gold text-[14px] md:text-[15px] font-medium tracking-[1.4px] uppercase mb-6">
              60-Minute Session
            </p>

            <!-- Price -->
            <div class="mb-6">
              <span class="font-aktiv text-kd-navy text-[48px] md:text-[56px] font-bold leading-none">$275</span>
              <span class="font-montserrat text-kd-grey text-[14px] md:text-[15px] font-light ml-2">USD</span>
            </div>

            <!-- What's included -->
            <ul class="space-y-3 mb-8">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-kd-gold flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                </svg>
                <span class="font-montserrat text-black text-[15px] leading-[24px] font-light">AI implementation strategy for your e-commerce brand</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-kd-gold flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                </svg>
                <span class="font-montserrat text-black text-[15px] leading-[24px] font-light">How to leverage AI tools for retention marketing</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-kd-gold flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                </svg>
                <span class="font-montserrat text-black text-[15px] leading-[24px] font-light">Personalized AI workflow recommendations</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-kd-gold flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                </svg>
                <span class="font-montserrat text-black text-[15px] leading-[24px] font-light">Q&A on AI automation for email, SMS & marketing</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-kd-gold flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                </svg>
                <span class="font-montserrat text-black text-[15px] leading-[24px] font-light">Recording of the session for your records</span>
              </li>
            </ul>

            <!-- CTA Button - Links to Stripe -->
            <a
              href="https://buy.stripe.com/YOUR_STRIPE_PAYMENT_LINK"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
              class="btn-navy w-full py-4 px-6 rounded-lg text-[14px] md:text-[15px] font-montserrat font-medium tracking-[1.4px] uppercase flex items-center justify-center gap-3"
            >
              Book Your Session
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Right: Why book -->
        <div class="animate-on-scroll fade-in-up delay-100">
          <h3 class="font-aktiv text-kd-navy text-[20px] md:text-[24px] font-semibold tracking-[1px] mb-6">
            Why Book an AI Strategy Session?
          </h3>

          <div class="space-y-6">
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-aktiv text-kd-gold text-[16px] md:text-[17px] font-semibold tracking-[0.8px] mb-2">
                Learn From an AI Pioneer
              </h4>
              <p class="font-montserrat text-black text-[15px] leading-[26px] font-light">
                Get insights from the founder of the first AI-native retention marketing agency. Learn what's actually working with AI in e-commerce today.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div>
              <h4 class="font-aktiv text-kd-gold text-[16px] md:text-[17px] font-semibold tracking-[0.8px] mb-2">
                Skip the Learning Curve
              </h4>
              <p class="font-montserrat text-black text-[15px] leading-[26px] font-light">
                AI tools are evolving fast. One hour with an expert can save you months of trial-and-error figuring out what works for your business.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div>
              <h4 class="font-aktiv text-kd-gold text-[16px] md:text-[17px] font-semibold tracking-[0.8px] mb-2">
                Actionable, Not Theoretical
              </h4>
              <p class="font-montserrat text-black text-[15px] leading-[26px] font-light">
                Walk away with specific AI tools, workflows, and implementation steps you can use immediately—not vague concepts.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Who Is This For Section -->
  <section class="py-12 md:py-16 px-6" style="background: linear-gradient(180deg, #F6EFE6 0%, #FAFAFA 100%);">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="animate-on-scroll fade-in-up font-aktiv text-kd-navy text-[24px] md:text-[32px] font-semibold tracking-[1.2px] text-center mb-10">
        This Session Is Perfect For You If...
      </h2>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 md:gap-8">
        <div class="animate-on-scroll fade-in-up delay-100 bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-kd-gold/10 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-kd-gold" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7h8m0 0v8m0-8l-8 8-4-4-6 6" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <p class="font-montserrat text-black text-[15px] leading-[24px] font-light">
              You want to integrate AI into your marketing but don't know where to start
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="animate-on-scroll fade-in-up delay-200 bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-kd-gold/10 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-kd-gold" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <p class="font-montserrat text-black text-[15px] leading-[24px] font-light">
              You're curious about how AI can automate and improve your email & SMS workflows
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="animate-on-scroll fade-in-up delay-300 bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-kd-gold/10 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-kd-gold" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8.228 9c.549-1.165 2.03-2 3.772-2 2.21 0 4 1.343 4 3 0 1.4-1.278 2.575-3.006 2.907-.542.104-.994.54-.994 1.093m0 3h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <p class="font-montserrat text-black text-[15px] leading-[24px] font-light">
              You have specific questions about AI tools like Claude, ChatGPT, or Klaviyo AI
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="animate-on-scroll fade-in-up delay-400 bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-kd-gold/10 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-kd-gold" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <p class="font-montserrat text-black text-[15px] leading-[24px] font-light">
              You want to stay ahead of the competition by leveraging AI before they do
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Booking Section -->
  <section id="book-consultation" class="py-12 md:py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
      <h2 class="animate-on-scroll fade-in-up font-aktiv text-kd-navy text-[24px] md:text-[32px] font-semibold tracking-[1.2px] mb-4">
        Ready to Book?
      </h2>

      <p class="animate-on-scroll fade-in-up delay-100 font-montserrat text-black text-[16px] md:text-[17px] leading-[26px] font-light mb-8 max-w-xl mx-auto">
        Select a time that works for you. After booking, you'll receive a confirmation email with details on how to prepare for our session.
      </p>

      <!-- Calendar Embed Placeholder -->
      <div class="animate-on-scroll fade-in-up delay-200 bg-kd-cream rounded-xl p-8 md:p-12 min-h-[400px] flex items-center justify-center">
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-4 rounded-full bg-kd-gold/20 flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-kd-gold" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 7V3m8 4V3m-9 8h10M5 21h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <p class="font-montserrat text-kd-grey text-[15px] mb-4">
            Calendar booking widget will be embedded here
          </p>
          <p class="font-montserrat text-kd-grey text-[13px]">
            (Calendly, Cal.com, or similar)
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Alternative: Contact link -->
      <p class="animate-on-scroll fade-in-up delay-300 font-montserrat text-black text-[14px] mt-6">
        Have questions before booking? <a href="/contact" class="text-kd-gold hover:text-kd-navy transition-colors font-medium">Contact us</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ Section -->
  <section class="py-12 md:py-16 px-6" style="background: linear-gradient(180deg, #FAFAFA 0%, #F6EFE6 100%);">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="animate-on-scroll fade-in-up font-aktiv text-kd-navy text-[24px] md:text-[28px] font-semibold tracking-[1.2px] text-center mb-10">
        Frequently Asked Questions
      </h2>

      <div class="space-y-4">
        <!-- FAQ Item 1 -->
        <details class="animate-on-scroll fade-in-up delay-100 bg-white rounded-xl p-6 group">
          <summary class="font-aktiv text-kd-navy text-[16px] md:text-[17px] font-semibold tracking-[0.8px] cursor-pointer list-none flex items-center justify-between">
            How do I prepare for the consultation?
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-kd-gold transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" />
            </svg>
          </summary>
          <p class="font-montserrat text-black text-[15px] leading-[26px] font-light mt-4">
            After booking, you'll receive a short questionnaire to help me understand your business and goals. I recommend having access to your Klaviyo account during our call so we can review your setup together.
          </p>
        </details>

        <!-- FAQ Item 2 -->
        <details class="animate-on-scroll fade-in-up delay-200 bg-white rounded-xl p-6 group">
          <summary class="font-aktiv text-kd-navy text-[16px] md:text-[17px] font-semibold tracking-[0.8px] cursor-pointer list-none flex items-center justify-between">
            What if I need to reschedule?
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-kd-gold transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" />
            </svg>
          </summary>
          <p class="font-montserrat text-black text-[15px] leading-[26px] font-light mt-4">
            No problem! You can reschedule up to 24 hours before your session at no extra cost. Just use the link in your confirmation email.
          </p>
        </details>

        <!-- FAQ Item 3 -->
        <details class="animate-on-scroll fade-in-up delay-300 bg-white rounded-xl p-6 group">
          <summary class="font-aktiv text-kd-navy text-[16px] md:text-[17px] font-semibold tracking-[0.8px] cursor-pointer list-none flex items-center justify-between">
            Will I get a recording of the session?
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-kd-gold transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" />
            </svg>
          </summary>
          <p class="font-montserrat text-black text-[15px] leading-[26px] font-light mt-4">
            Yes! Every session is recorded and you'll receive the video within 24 hours. This way you can revisit our discussion and share it with your team.
          </p>
        </details>

        <!-- FAQ Item 4 -->
        <details class="animate-on-scroll fade-in-up delay-400 bg-white rounded-xl p-6 group">
          <summary class="font-aktiv text-kd-navy text-[16px] md:text-[17px] font-semibold tracking-[0.8px] cursor-pointer list-none flex items-center justify-between">
            What happens after the consultation?
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-kd-gold transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" />
            </svg>
          </summary>
          <p class="font-montserrat text-black text-[15px] leading-[26px] font-light mt-4">
            You'll have a clear action plan to implement. If you'd like ongoing support, we can discuss our full-service retention marketing packages—but there's absolutely no obligation.
          </p>
        </details>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
